# Copy to .env.local and set the gateway URL to enable real network from
# the in-browser python guest. Without these, wasi:sockets/tcp falls
# back to the virtual implementation (NotSupported) -- non-network code
# (zlib/sqlite/hashlib/openssl ctx creation) still works fine.
#
# Run the gateway: node web/ws-gateway-server.mjs
#
# VITE_TCP_GATEWAY_URL=ws://127.0.0.1:8088/ws
# VITE_TCP_GATEWAY_TOKEN=  # optional bearer-style auth (gateway ignores in dev build)
